name: Space Chaos (itch) (Milk4Lyfe)
description:
In this slightly physic friendly game, you play as an UFO and plan on going to Mars! However, there is gray UFOs blocking the path.  Your objective is to clear out the path... in the CHAOS WAY.

Note: There is an issue with the resolution, please use fullscreen for now. Also, there is no mobile support for now.
